              </svg>
              <div>
                <span class="text-text-default font-medium">一个目标明确的销售团队：</span>
                <span class="text-text-default">每个销售人员都清楚自己的具体任务和指标。</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 25 25" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <circle cx="12.5" cy="12.5" r="12.5" fill="white" />
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd"
                  d="M12.5 0C5.59659 0 0 5.59659 0 12.5C0 19.4034 5.59659 25 12.5 25C19.4034 25 25 19.4034 25 12.5C25 5.59659 19.4034 0 12.5 0ZM17.9182 10.3864C18.018 10.2723 18.0939 10.1395 18.1416 9.99565C18.1892 9.85182 18.2077 9.6999 18.1958 9.54885C18.1839 9.39779 18.1419 9.25064 18.0722 9.11605C18.0026 8.98147 17.9068 8.86216 17.7904 8.76516C17.674 8.66816 17.5394 8.59541 17.3944 8.55121C17.2495 8.507 17.0972 8.49223 16.9465 8.50776C16.7957 8.52329 16.6496 8.5688 16.5168 8.64163C16.3839 8.71445 16.2669 8.81312 16.1727 8.93182L11.2864 14.7943L8.75795 12.2648C8.54363 12.0578 8.25659 11.9432 7.95864 11.9458C7.66068 11.9484 7.37567 12.0679 7.16498 12.2786C6.95429 12.4893 6.83478 12.7743 6.83219 13.0723C6.8296 13.3702 6.94414 13.6573 7.15114 13.8716L10.5602 17.2807C10.6719 17.3923 10.8056 17.4794 10.9527 17.5364C11.0999 17.5935 11.2574 17.6193 11.4151 17.6121C11.5728 17.6049 11.7272 17.565 11.8686 17.4948C12.0101 17.4247 12.1353 17.3258 12.2364 17.2045L17.9182 10.3864Z"
                  fill="#024340" />
              </svg>
              <div>
                <span class="text-text-default font-medium">一个可预测的销售漏斗：</span>
                <span class="text-text-default">让收入增长变得更加稳定和可持续。</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- CTA Button -->
          <div data-aos="fade-up-sm" data-aos-delay="300">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="relative mt-8 flex items-center"
            >
              <span class="btn btn-outline btn-outline-primary has-text-flip-animation before:btn before:btn-outline-primary after:btn after:btn-outline-primary">
                点击预约60分钟战略通话
              </span>
              <span class="icon">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Right content - Image (mobile second, then left on desktop) -->
        <div class="has-animated-number relative lg:pt-8 pb-0 lg:order-1">
          <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto w-fit" data-aos="fade-up-sm">
            <img
              class="max-w-full md:max-w-lg"
              src="/images/call-to-action/sparkliang.webp"
              alt="专家顾问"
            />
            <!-- Experience badge -->
            <div class="bg-primary absolute bottom-16 right-20 md:right-0">
              <div class="py-2 ps-5 text-white">
                <div class="relative flex items-stretch">
                  <div class="text-h2 leading-tight font-bold text-inherit md:text-6xl">
                    利<small><small>润+</small></small>
                  </div>
                  <sup class="font-secondary top-0 -left-6 text-sm font-bold tracking-wider text-inherit">
                    不用靠猜的
                  </sup>
                </div>
                <img
                  class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 h-full w-full"
                  src="/images/call-to-action/stats-block-bg.svg"
                  alt="background pattern"
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Background shape -->
          <div class="bg-primary pointer-events-none absolute top-[calc(50%_-_42px)] left-1/2 h-[35.875rem] w-[35.875rem] -translate-x-1/2 rounded-full opacity-80" />
        </div>
      </div>
